      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="main_title__text">
        <h2 data-splitting>
          BEST OF THE WORLD <br />
          STX Engineering & Construction
        </h2>
        <p>세계최고를 향해 STX건설이 힘차게 질주합니다!</p>
      </div>
